This project Status : Competed.

This project is a live "Secret" app where you can resigter , login and create post your secrets anonymously.

*Functionalities Used :

-Fronend : html, css, bootstrap

-backend : Node.js, express and ejs

-Database: mongoDB, Monodb-Atlas (For databse server support)

-Security: Passport.js Authentication and Google OAuth 2.0 (Which adds a signUp and Login Feature through your google account


Live WebApp Link : https://mighty-peak-00882.herokuapp.com/
